genresAdvancedInfo.name: cuban funk
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Cuban funk is a funky, groovy genre that incorporates elements of Cuban music, soul, and jazz. The music is characterized by its upbeat tempo, funky basslines, and brass sections. Cuban funk is perfect for getting people up and dancing, and is often played at parties and festivals.
